---
title: Jumbo Shrimp and Bacon Étouffée-Style Stew with Spinach Rice Pilaf
description: Juicy jumbo shrimp are given the "etouffée" treatment by being smothered in a flavourful sauce studded by the holy trinity of Cajun aromatics: celery, onion and green peppers.
